---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const portfolios = [
  {
    name: "John Ray Jordan",
    classYear: "Class of 2032",
    focus: "Distance & Breaststroke",
    href: "https://app.outcomestar.app/john",
  },
];
---

<Layout title="OutcomeStar">
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-navy-950 via-navy-900/40 to-navy-950"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(240,120,0,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(32,24,104,0.4) 0%, transparent 50%);"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-flame mb-8">OutcomeStar</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-light text-white mb-8 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
        A documented record of every outcome that earned the seat.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-light">
        Each student carries a portfolio of academic, athletic, and leadership evidence built year over year. OutcomeStar is the place that record lives &mdash; citable, comparable, and ready for the people who decide.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-y border-slate-800/50 bg-navy-900/30">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-flame mb-8">Current portfolios</p>
      <ul class="divide-y divide-slate-800/60">
        {portfolios.map((p) => (
          <li>
            <a href={p.href} class="group flex items-baseline justify-between gap-6 py-5 hover:bg-slate-900/30 -mx-4 px-4 rounded transition-colors">
              <div>
                <p class="text-white text-lg font-medium group-hover:text-flame transition-colors">{p.name}</p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">{p.classYear} &middot; {p.focus}</p>
              </div>
              <span class="text-slate-600 group-hover:text-flame transition-colors text-sm">View &rarr;</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-flame mb-4">What it is</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light mb-8 leading-tight">
        Evidence, organized once. Used everywhere it counts.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-light">
        <p>Selective universities, scholarship committees, and recruiting coaches don't decide on a transcript alone. They look at the full record &mdash; the trajectory of academic work, athletic results, leadership roles, and the through-line that connects who a student was in middle school to who they're becoming in twelfth grade.</p>
        <p>Families know this. But the record sits scattered across email threads, results sites, coach DMs, school portals, and screenshots on a parent's phone. By application season it's irretrievable.</p>
        <p class="text-white">OutcomeStar is the system of record. Capture once. Cite forever.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-navy-900/30 border-y border-slate-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="border border-flame/30 bg-flame/5 rounded-lg p-8 md:p-10">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-flame mb-3">Roach Middle School pilot &middot; Free through 2027</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-light mb-4 leading-tight">Frisco ISD families: this is for you.</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">
          OutcomeStar is opening to Roach Middle School families as a free pilot through the 2026-2027 school year. Sign up with your student's Frisco ISD email and start the record now &mdash; not when applications are due.
        </p>
        <a href="/signup" class="inline-block bg-flame hover:bg-flame/90 text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded transition-colors">Join the pilot</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white font-light mb-4 leading-tight">Start the record.</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 font-light">Free for Roach Middle School families through 2027.</p>
      <a href="/signup" class="inline-block bg-flame hover:bg-flame/90 text-white font-medium px-10 py-4 rounded text-lg transition-colors">Get started</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>